    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>People who are famous or had significant roles in history; also, those who are not necessarily famous, but whose existence is recorded, as distinguished from those who are fictional or legendary.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
